    "description": "IFIS Japan Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, researches and estimates data in Japan. It operates through five segments: Investment Information Business, Document Solutions Business, Fund Disclosure Lawyer Business, IT Solution Business, and Language Solutions Business. The company provides electronic distribution services for securities research reports; corporate earning forecasts and consensus data services; financial document production and printing services; and system integration services for financial institutions. It also offers DX solutions, including robot advisor, document management, financial document order system, automatic pamphlet creation system, terms/contract creation system, operation report creation system, life plan simulation, communication portal, information sheet creation tool, web to print, and PIP maker solutions. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan."
